Package: DeLuciatoR
Type: Package
Title: Make R Plots Match DeLucia Publication Specs
Version: 0.1.3
Date: 2016-12-07
Author: Chris Black
Maintainer: Chris Black <chris@ckblack.org>
Description: Tools to help the DeLucia lab make R plots look the way Evan wants them. Notable changes from R defaults include much larger text, horizontal y-axis numbering, 4:3 panel aspect ratio, inward-facing ticks on all sides, colors always dichromat-safe & used only when necessary.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
	ggplot2 (>= 1.0.0)
Imports:
	grid
Suggests:
	ggplotTicks (>= 0.0.2),
	gridExtra
